data.description: Rare 5 Acres Home & Outbuildings nestled amoung trees. Equestrian/Mini Farm/Homestead, peace & quiet away from city. Fenced & cross-fenced pastures w/ lean-to run along private drive. Enjoy garden, fruit trees, chicken coop, dog run, wildlife, fire pits & shop w/ meat processing rm, 2 bays, workshop w/ wood stove & bonus rm. Near hunting, hiking, trails, fishing, and public access/boat ramps to 3 lakes. Mainfloor 3 bd/2 ba, LR, kitchen, DR & partial wrapping deck. Daylight bsmt feats spacious family room w/ cooktop wood stove & kitchenette, 1 ba, laundry, 2 bonus rooms & 4th bd. Lots of parking, patios for bbq/entertaining. Newer SS range/stove, microwave & dishwasher. Newer pipes & well pump. Fiber Optic Highspeed Internet const underway.
